# Download

To download Glucky Wars you can just follow the next steeps.

1- go to Glucky Wars official web site (www.gluckywars.com). 

2- slow down a little bit and you will find a section called: "Download!".

3- press the button that say download and wait.

4- After the download, open the launcher and create a new account.

5- after it go to the library and press download. You will download the game.

6- When the download its done, you just need to press on the button to play.

We are waiting for you! Come and play Glucky Wars!
